=== BagavadgItAyAM 2.22 ===

--- line ---
vAsAMsi[clothes] jIrRAni[worn out] yaTA[just as] vihAya[leaving behind]
navAni[new] gfhRAti[takes] naraH[a man]+aparARi[others]=naro'parARi .

"Just as a man casts off worn out clothes"
"Just as a man takes "

--- line ---
taTA SarIrARi vihAya jIrRA
nyanyAni saMyAti navAni dehI .. 22 ..
